## My C++ Work 

### Generic Programming & The STL

I am experienced with the use of the STL in C++ as well as the concepts and application of 'generic programming.' This page is supposed to include my school work in C++ but by request by Professor Glenn Downing of the University of Texas, my school work and github repositories by his wishes need to remain private due to future semesters of the class. If you are a recruiter wishing to see my C++ work, please email me and I can add you as a collaborator to all the related repositories so you can view my source code.
